{"tid":627713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（又入波）警長拍女下屬臀判罰款","createTime":"2018-04-13T08:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T10:39:23.000Z","uid":54337,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e24938bcbb742822116b56f211737da2f91fc8cb","tid":627713,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.pbh2.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/muller.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbh2.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F12%2Fmuller.gif&h=8c5f3a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警長拍女下屬臀判罰款　官指定罪穩妥駁回上訴<br />\n<br />\n04月13日(五) 15:39<br />\n<br />\n已婚男警署警長前年當值期間，被指在報案中心內向女下屬搣臉頰和耳珠，又手捉女下屬手臂令她自打臀部，涉案53歲被告蔡德祥被裁定3項普通襲擊罪成立，罰款9000港元，他早前提出上訴，指原審裁判官出錯。原訟庭法官今頒判詞駁回，維持原判。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蔡在上訴宗卷中，多方面批評原審裁判官考慮證供沒有公平考慮蔡的證供，忽略考慮蔡「真誠相信女事主接受他的行為」的辯解，相反輕易接納女事主的證言。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原訟庭法官認為，蔡對裁判官的批評屬吹毛求疵，且斷章取義及矯枉過正，直言裁判官已全盤考慮全部證人的證供，且清晰交代接納或拒絕接納的原因，其裁判無錯誤之處，定罪穩妥，遂駁回上訴。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"8d7fca7a8a7265de1393036ae76ff51b7a70df70","tid":627713,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:14:06.000Z","msg":"個龍係咪錯判，好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaf483019a59f005d641686628794f0b2f65d6a","tid":627713,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:26:20.000Z","msg":"警長犯三項普通襲擊罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算入一球定三球？"},{"pid":"ddbe640418aa584147f1ca3c6ca77208d5701f12","tid":627713,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"333631ffc3e9358c287c7d341b5eacbbd6a69d8c","tid":627713,"uid":99568,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"